// {{interpolation}} (e.g. {{name}}, {{score}}, {{count}}, {{n}}, {{weaknesses}},
// {{link}}) is substituted at render time.
// Brand / tool names (DeftBrain, deftbrain.com, NameStorm) stay verbatim in
// every language. The audited NAME itself is user input and is NEVER keyed/
// translated. TLD strings (.com, .io), social platform names (X, Instagram,
// TikTok) and language/region proper names returned by the API are proper
// nouns — kept verbatim, NOT keyed.
// The "— Generated by DeftBrain · deftbrain.com" suffix is added in code via
// BRAND — not in keys. Emoji rendered in JSX next to a label stays OUT of the
// string; emoji embedded inside a value (nav labels, pill labels, copy-text
// headers) is intentional and kept inside the string.
